lf in a match that could be the last encounter between two of the biggest-ever tennis champions.\", \"from\": 663, \"to\": 889, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Djokovic\", \"from\": 663, \"to\": 671}, {\"ngram\": \"24 Grand Slam\", \"from\": 685, \"to\": 698}, {\"ngram\": \"titles\", \"from\": 707, \"to\": 713}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 734, \"to\": 741}, {\"ngram\": \"a flawless display\", \"from\": 755, \"to\": 773}, {\"ngram\": \"a set\", \"from\": 779, \"to\": 784}, {\"ngram\": \"a half\", \"from\": 789, \"to\": 795}, {\"ngram\": \"a match\", \"from\": 799, \"to\": 806}, {\"ngram\": \"the last encounter\", \"from\": 821, \"to\": 839}, {\"ngram\": \"the biggest-ever tennis champions\", \"from\": 855, \"to\": 888}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The world No.\", \"from\": 891, \"to\": 904, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The world No\", \"from\": 891, \"to\": 903}]}, {\"sentence\": \"2 stretched the 38-year-old Spaniard with punishing groundstrokes and perfect drop shots, making him look his age as he raced through the first set, 6-1, and went 4-0 up in the second.\", \"from\": 905, \"to\": 1089, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 933, \"end\": 941, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\", \"score\": 0.6256405728118872, \"rank\": 0.5983552387323885, \"text\": \"Spaniard\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"groundstrokes\", \"from\": 957, \"to\": 970}, {\"ngram\": \"perfect drop shots\", \"from\": 975, \"to\": 993}, {\"ngram\": \"his age\", \"from\": 1011, \"to\": 1018}, {\"ngram\": \"the first set\", \"from\": 1039, \"to\": 1052}, {\"ngram\": \"the second\", \"from\": 1078, \"to\": 1088}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The home crowd was ready for a mouth-watering epic between two of the greatest players to have graced the sport on their record-extending 60th encounter, but instead, they were being treated to what looked like a fast-track Djokovic win.\", \"from\": 1091, \"to\": 1328, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1315, \"end\": 1323, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.190684456311305e-18, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The home crowd\", \"from\": 1091, \"to\": 1105}, {\"ngram\": \"a mouth-watering epic\", \"from\": 1120, \"to\": 1141}, {\"ngram\": \"the greatest players\", \"from\": 1157, \"to\": 1177}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 1193, \"to\": 1202}, {\"ngram\": \"their record-extending 60th encounter\", \"from\": 1206, \"to\": 1243}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nadal, with his thigh strapped due to a recent injury, was spilling unforced errors across Court Philipp Chatrier, a venue he has dominated like no other player, and lacked precision and consistency.\", \"from\": 1330, \"to\": 1529, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nadal\", \"from\": 1330, \"to\": 1335}, {\"ngram\": \"his thigh\", \"from\": 1342, \"to\": 1351}, {\"ngram\": \"a recent injury\", \"from\": 1368, \"to\": 1383}, {\"ngram\": \"unforced errors\", \"from\": 1398, \"to\": 1413}, {\"ngram\": \"Court Philipp Chatrier\", \"from\": 1421, \"to\": 1443}, {\"ngram\": \"a venue\", \"from\": 1445, \"to\": 1452}, {\"ngram\": \"no other player\", \"from\": 1475, \"to\": 1490}, {\"ngram\": \"precision\", \"from\": 1503, \"to\": 1512}, {\"ngram\": \"consistency\", \"from\": 1517, \"to\": 1528}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Early in the second set he had 13 errors, almost three times as many as Djokovic's five.\", \"from\": 1531, \"to\": 1619, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the second set\", \"from\": 1540, \"to\": 1554}, {\"ngram\": \"13 errors\", \"from\": 1562, \"to\": 1571}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Shaking his head in d